  &lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="https://www.gov.uk/technical-guidance-for-transport-stats#road-congestion-and-reliability-statistics"&gt;An introduction into the Department for Transport’s congestion statistics&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
  &lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="https://www.gov.uk/technical-guidance-for-transport-stats#road-congestion-and-reliability-statistics"&gt;Methodology for calculation of reliability on Highways Agency’s motorway and ‘A’ road network&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;h2 id="further-information"&gt;Further information&lt;/h2&gt;

&lt;ul&gt;
