    <title>BIS monthly spend October 2012</title>
    <category>Publication</category>
    <summary>BIS spending data for October 2012.</summary>
    <content type="html">&lt;div class="govspeak"&gt;&lt;p&gt;The government is committed to setting new standards for transparency so the public can more easily see how and where taxpayers’ money is being spent and hold politicians, government departments and public bodies to account. &lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;All central government departments must publish details of their spending over £25,000, and publish monthly information by the last day of each month.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</content>
